title: I am having trouble with my new pixel 4a
content: I have a new pixel 4a.  I have two email accounts.  Due to some reason google has set up a work profile.  As I have to add one to this work profile and one to my personal account I only have half of my contacts that I can access on my phone.  All this worked wonderfully on my Pixel 2.  I have contacted Google support and in a polite manner shrugged their shoulders and said try here.
category: Setting up and Personalizing your Device
